 Silver, Lee M. (1997). "Genetics Goes to Hollywood". Nature Genetics. 17 (3): 260–261. doi:10.1038/ng1197-260. S2CID 29335234.
 Anderson, W. French (1990). "Genetics and Human Malleability." The Hastings Center Report, 20(1), 21–24. doi:10.2307/3562969 p.24
 Zimmer, Carl (10 November 2008). "Now: The Rest of the Genome". The New York Times.
